Class StorageCredentialsToken

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.storage.StorageCredentials

  • public final class StorageCredentialsToken

      • StorageCredentialsToken

        public StorageCredentialsToken(String accountName,
                       String token)
        Creates an instance of the StorageCredentialsToken class, using the specified token. Token credentials must only be used with HTTPS requests on the blob and queue services. The specified token is stored as a String.
        Parameters:
        token - A String that represents the token.
